<content type="application/x.deki0805+xml" title="caption"><body xmlns:eval="http://mindtouch.com/2007/dekiscript"><div class="noinclude"><span class="script">template.XULRefElem()</span></div> <p>A header for a <span class="script">template.XULElem("groupbox")</span>. It may contain either a text label, using the <span class="script">template.XULAttr("label")</span> attribute, or child elements for a more complex caption.
</p><p>More information is available in the <a href="en/XUL_Tutorial/Groupboxes">XUL tutorial</a>.
</p>
